Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:03.11,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:06.38,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was forced to take a pill that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:07.62,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.35,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My mind is that of a former great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.92,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case takes place at an art museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.65,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Behind the scenes is a grisly, red death!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.71,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No matter the incident,\Nthere is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.90,Dialogue Top,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Medieval Art Exhibit"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:03.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Patrolling an art museum at night is the last thing I wanted to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:06.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never make a good watchman with an attitude like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:09.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't tease me like that, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-It came from this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:37.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A medieval suit of armor? All by itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Two watchmen saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we all go there right now? It sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:56.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The museum obviously cooked that story up to bring in more visitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:03:01.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Only kids would fall for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.22,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And you're not a kid all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, time to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran always gets like that when she gets mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't have let her learn karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:25.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Medieval Art Exhibit"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these beautiful paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we came!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! The colors are so lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:47.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you like that painting, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, enjoy this painting very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:54.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I love all of the paintings here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as if they were my own children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where are my manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ochiai. I run this art gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I should have known!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy your visit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kubota! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:23.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I said to wear gloves when handling exhibits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:26.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Iijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Please take over for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As empty and quiet as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ten days left until this place shuts down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:47.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of all this moldy, old junk for me until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK, architect. Bring the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This art gallery is going to close for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The previous owner's company went bankrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:03.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so he sold this place to that Mr. Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:06.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He sold it under the agreement that Mr. Manaka would keep it running!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then the instant he bought it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,he said he was going to turn it into a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:19.16,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's carelessly handling another exhibit again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you're Kubota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:26.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you hurry and scrape whatever money you can get together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.41,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:42.45,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why didn't he get angry again just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:46.34,Character Card,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:50.30,Character Card,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:54.27,Character Card,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. There's supposed to be another room up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about it. Let's hurry and get through this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about pathetic! Getting exhausted so easily like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:31.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The no entrance sign is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:35.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Since we're here,\Nwhy don't we go see the last room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can go home if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll have to cook dinner yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,- That's not fair!\N- That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:51.28,Character Card,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hell Gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:56.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This room sure is dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is the Hell Gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:08.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It literally is a picture from Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The title is "Divine Punishment".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:17.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It says it's a picture of a knight of justice sealing away a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mr. Manaka, the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:38.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I assure you, I haven't allowed anyone to touch the corpse, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, did anyone see who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:53.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. I've checked with everyone, but no one saw a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That security camera might have caught the person on tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid murderer. Being caught on tape without knowing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Time to come out, killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:16.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us have a good look at your face—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this scene somewhere before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly like in that painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The picture on display directly across from the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The title was "Divine Punishment".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer must have killed him in this manner
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to make it look exactly like that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a daring murderer, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It would be all over if someone saw them wearing that around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:14.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, there was a no-entry sign in front of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. That was around 4 o'clock, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But when we passed by just after 5:00, the sign was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place at approximately 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:31.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem it was the murderer who put the sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After doing that to keep people away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:36.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the murderer put the armor on and hid in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:40.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then killed Mr. Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:44.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the killer was someone well acquainted with the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:50.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the killer is one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:54.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! The owner's doing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't be messing with the tape without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:03.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He's doing something before the killer jumped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He realized something and took that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then the pen on top of the desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's writing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He threw the pen away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:13.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about the card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:14.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Crumpled up in his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Does that card say what I think it might?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It might still be in his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found this piece of paper in the victim's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kubota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's my name doing on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:42.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you wore the armor to conceal your identity from the camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but it also seems that the victim wasn't so easily fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:54.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, give us your alibi. Where were you at 4:30?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:59.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was alone in the office, doing work that Mr. Ochiai asked me to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.64,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did ask him to do some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means nobody saw you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:11.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! What motive would I have for killing the owner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:13.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to talk your way out of this, Kubota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:16.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The owner threatened to sue you for damages
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:20.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,because you were secretly selling this museum's exhibits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:26.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that had nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the one who killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:35.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The truth will come to light once my men find the suit of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:42.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure! There's a ballpoint pen over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a nice pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That pen was created this year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:57.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In celebration of Beika Art Museum's 50th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:12:00.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who works here has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So someone accidentally left it here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Both colors and widths are exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the one the victim used.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.71,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:22.92,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Kubota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} should have known about the security camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.92,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}so why did he choose this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:29.26,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}especially if it meant wearing armor to conceal his identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.96,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}To make it look like that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:37.13,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, he doesn't seem to have much interest in art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:41.62,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Would such a person actually do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's straight out of a horror movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:53.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, little boy! You can't just barge in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:57.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure says he wants you to help with something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He must've figured out we really wanted to watch the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is where it starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the card that he's so shocked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he throw the pen away when he finished writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:35.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The killer would have realized he was there if he made any sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! When I found the pen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the tip was retracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnatural for someone who's about to be killed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:55.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to retract the pen tip of a twist-style ballpoint pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.91,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's a mark on the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.88,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.48,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now I have this trick figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! We found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We found the armor in Kubota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You found it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy! I don't know anything about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have two major pieces of evidence that point to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:42.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This blood-smeared suit of armor, and the victim's dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.34,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No! That isn't a dying message at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.40,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's a trick the killer used to put the blame on Kubota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was one bloody attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that this work of art was ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's a replica used for decoration purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was the same one Kubota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was moving this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:08.86,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah, so it was a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.07,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's why the museum manager didn't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.80,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}when he handled the armor so violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:19.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The replica was used in the attack, so the real one wasn't ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:23.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seems none of the other exhibits have been touched, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:26.21,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come to think of it, the wall where he was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.69,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...had cards, but no paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.76,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The killer removed them in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:39.40,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}To protect them from the blood during the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:43.93,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The killer really was one of the staff members!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:45.60,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:50.94,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is a trick that doesn't work without nulling Kubota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:55.21,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means the one behind it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:58.11,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...must be the museum manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.45,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If my conclusions are correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:04.05,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}there's a possibility the murderer might still have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kubota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you'll have to come down to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom! Bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Where's the bathroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:27.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The restroom? Go out this room,\Ngo down the stairs on your right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and then—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's too complicated for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Draw it on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:39.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, you go out this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:49.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you writing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:55.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You knew before writing anything that that pen doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:59.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's strange. Why did you have a pen that you knew didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A ballpoint pen that doesn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:08.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If Mr. Manaka was also using a pen that doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:12.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,then this dying message should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's a strange mark left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:23.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like someone scribbled over the letters with a pen that didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What if that mark was left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,because someone tried to cross out the letters beneath it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but the pen didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:39.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! This wasn't written by Mr. Manaka at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:44.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was written beforehand by none other than the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then why did he take the card in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:53.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The killer told the owner the following:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:57.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at the card behind you!\NThe name of your murderer is on it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:03.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the card had Kubota's name on it,\Nnot the name of the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:10.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shocked, he tried to cross out the name\Nand replace it with the real one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,using the ballpoint pen on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:17.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That pen had been placed there in advance by the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and it didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:26.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why he threw the pen away and tried to crumple up the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In short, this was all a trick to fool us,\Nperpetrated by the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:35.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,using a pen without ink\Nand a video tape without sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:43.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the pen we found does work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:47.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the tip of that pen retracted when we found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Strange for someone who's about to be killed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to go through all the trouble of retracting a pen's tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:19:00.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the killer switched this pen\Nwith the other one after the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:04.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but carelessly forgot to put the pen tip out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:09.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means whoever's currently in possession of a pen that doesn't work
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is the one responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:12.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:18.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it was you, Mr. Ochiai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear your alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you at 4:30 when the murder took place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ochiai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:33.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting to meet someone at 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:37.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for that black-hearted demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:40.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...while inside that suit of armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:46.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happened afterward\Nis exactly as you said, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing everything was caught on tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:54.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was no accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:57.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Having Mr. Manaka stand where he did, the timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:01.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the location of the card, the location of the pen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They were all done according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:07.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced here on several occasions, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then the rumor about the security guards
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,seeing the suit of armor walking late at night was real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it was a foolish thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:21.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but I did it for the purpose\Nof getting rid of Mr. Manaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:25.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the demon who was going to\Nshut down this divine museum
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:31.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and take away from me all of these exhibits that are like my own children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:35.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then there was Kubota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nwho went and sold some of my exhibits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:38.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to punish you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be different from the picture. Mr. Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:44.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've been struck down\Nby divine punishment as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:47.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is exactly like the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:51.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Although the knight of justice has slain the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:54.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,he has also been covered in its evil blood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:58.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,which will soak into him\Nand make him wicked in turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, I am a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:06.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, have become a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I was unable to deceive the small knight of justice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is proof enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The small knight of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, little boy. Do you not need to go to the restroom anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:13.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The art museum's not going to close after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:16.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. The citizens all got together after they heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:21.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. We don't have many cultural spots around here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:24.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:27.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sick of what, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:30.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's always Conan and that old man Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:33.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We never get to help out at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:34.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's because—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:35.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:36.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard the story at school
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:39.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,about the biology room skeleton coming to life at midnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:41.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:43.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One of the teachers saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:44.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the heart was still...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:48.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK! This is a case that calls for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break into school later tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:55.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! You better come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:57.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:06.15,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:06.15,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,60 seconds until the next episode's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:13.96,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's no doubt about it! He's the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:17.20,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But what's with that big smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:21.63,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just what sort of alibi does he have in that camera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.63,0:24:23.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I took this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:29.76,Dialogue Top,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.76,0:24:34.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Disposable Camera
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.93,0:24:38.25,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be stunned by the next episode's surprising trick!
